[48.463369, "o", "\r\n  Threat Model: Organization\r\n  Vertical: Healthcare & Life Sciences\r\n  ========================================================\r\n\r\n  Stack (3 tools):\r\n    - CrowdStrike Falcon (edr)\r\n    - Splunk Enterprise Security (siem)\r\n"]
[48.463394, "o", "    - Okta (iam)\r\n\r\n  Coverage: 75% (6/8 priority techniques)\r\n\r\n  Covered Techniques:\r\n    [T1486] Data Encrypted for Impact\r\n      Covered by: CrowdStrike Falcon\r\n    [T1490] Inhibit System Recovery\r\n      Covered by: CrowdStrike Falcon\r\n    [T1021.001] Remote Desktop Protocol\r\n      Covered by: CrowdStrike Falcon\r\n    [T1059.001] PowerShell\r\n      Covered by: CrowdStrike Falcon\r\n"]
[48.463411, "o", "    [T1070.001] Clear Windows Event Logs\r\n      Covered by: CrowdStrike Falcon, Splunk Enterprise Security\r\n    [T1562.001] Disable or Modify Tools\r\n      Covered by: CrowdStrike Falcon, Splunk Enterprise Security\r\n\r\n  Gaps (2 uncovered):\r\n"]
[48.463516, "o", "    [T1566.001] Spearphishing Attachment\r\n      Primary initial access vector for healthcare ransomware campaigns\r\n      Suggested: email\r\n    [T1048] Exfiltration Over Alternative Protocol\r\n      PHI exfiltration for double extortion — HIPAA breach notification trigger\r\n      Suggested: ndr, dlp\r\n\r\n  Compliance:\r\n    HIPAA: COVERED (crowdstrike, splunk, okta)\r\n    HITECH: GAP\r\n    FDA 21 CFR Part 11: GAP\r\n    NIST CSF: COVERED (crowdstrike, splunk, okta)\r\n\r\n  Threat Actors: LockBit, BlackCat/ALPHV, Clop, Royal, Hive\r\n\r\n  Recommendations:\r\n    [HIGH] Add email coverage for T1566.001 (Spearphishing Attachment)\r\n      Primary initial access vector for healthcare ransomware campaigns. Consider: Proofpoint, Mimecast, abnormal\r\n    [MEDIUM] Add ndr, dlp coverage for T1048 (Exfiltration Over Alternative Protocol)\r\n      PHI exfiltration for double extortion — HIPAA breach notification trigger. Consider: Darktrace, Vectra AI, symantec-dlp\r\n    [HIGH] Address HITECH compliance gap\r\n      No tools in your stack co"]
[48.463523, "o", "ver HITECH. Review vendor certifications.\r\n    [HIGH] Address FDA 21 CFR Part 11 compliance gap\r\n      No tools in your stack cover FDA 21 CFR Part 11. Review vendor certifications.\r\n\r\n"]
